Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.23,0:00:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.77,0:00:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.92,0:00:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.79,0:00:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.93,0:00:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.03,0:00:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.90,0:00:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.68,0:00:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.58,0:00:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.92,0:01:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.50,0:01:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好,前幾天對妳做出了\N非常失禮的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.04,0:02:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是,那個時候\N我絕對沒有不軌的企圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點希望妳能明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.45,0:02:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事讓我沈痛地領悟到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.99,0:02:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須積極去面對\N人生中最大的難題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.40,0:02:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大的難題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個難題解決之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.71,0:02:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能暫時無法和妳見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時無法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道連三鷹也放棄我了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.36,0:02:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#61 五代快追上去\N響子失戀的隻身之旅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼,要出門嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.01,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們昨晚發生了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.88,0:03:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上五代站在走廊\N一直看著妳的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼無精打采的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.86,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.16,0:03:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道妳要去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,偶爾也出去散散心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟妳還年輕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.84,0:03:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,散散心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.12,0:04:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?要去旅行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.42,0:04:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,我想去個三、四天左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.76,0:04:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我第一次單獨去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.23,0:04:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.70,0:04:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,聽說妳要去旅行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是羨慕死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個\N過來幫她計劃一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.82,0:04:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.45,0:04:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛,現在這個季節\N還是去北海道最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對啦,去沖繩啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以游泳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.70,0:05:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得去北海道最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.73,0:05:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是去信州吃碗蕎麥麵吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.34,0:05:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是沖繩好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的毛蟹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-沖繩的泡盛酒\N-信州的蕎麥麵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-毛蟹\N-泡盛酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.18,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用想那麼多\N快去準備行李吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,東北也不錯\N那裡的酒很棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,九州的酒也很好喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.93,0:05:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那信州要怎麼辦?\N我還是覺得信州最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.60,0:05:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們該不會是打算跟著來吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.60,0:05:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法,只好採納大家的意見\N這些地方全部都去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贊成!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你們不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.58,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用你們幫忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真是難伺候啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.40,0:06:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有回一刻館嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.60,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.73,0:06:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.60,0:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個婆娘耶,動不動就哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我啦,是管理員哭了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.19,0:06:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把行程還有旅館的電話\N都寫在這裡面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.97,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妳這幾天不在\N這棟公寓也不會垮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.24,0:06:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,萬一有什麼緊急的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.10,0:06:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心,萬一真有什麼事\N遠水也救不了近火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之,我把它貼在門上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨妳高興就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.08,0:07:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣都好,快點出發吧\N不然會來不及喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.56,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還搞不懂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…怎麼可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照你剛才所說的分析一下\N事情就是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,畢竟這是你跟管理員的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.81,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用常理分析可能行不通吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.26,0:07:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.73,0:07:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也並不是沒有想到這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.33,0:07:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,照常理來說的確是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.38,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會突然去旅行了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.37,0:08:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在你身邊,你也不要緊是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得問個清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要問清楚\N她為什麼要哭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.25,0:09:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,再來三杯啤酒,大杯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.22,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小姐,有沒有涼拌魚肉絲?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.06,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,妳怎麼啦?\N怎麼都不喝呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.57,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛\N這是特別為妳舉辦的送別會耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在胡扯什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為在這裡喝酒\N我才沒有趕上電車的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一班也快來不及了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.88,0:09:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去的就讓它過去吧\N上野車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.79,0:09:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯,來,喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是真的不讓我走嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.46,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算錯過兩三班電車\N鐵路又不會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒來了,酒來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.54,0:10:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.31,0:10:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一點酒,馬上就又喝光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.14,0:10:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-小姐,有沒有大杯的?\N-大杯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.38,0:10:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.93,0:10:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我去一下洗手間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,妳想溜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10號月台的乘客請趕快上車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.94,0:10:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,21點15分由上野到金澤的\N特快車即將開車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,車門即將關上,請小心注意安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.23,0:11:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像半夜跑路似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,嘴巴張開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,請妳等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會克服怕狗的毛病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比她晚了很久才出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.89,0:12:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,我一定會追上妳的\N管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.41,0:13:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他觀光客常去的地方還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.52,0:13:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,江戶村和檀風苑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.68,0:13:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點遠,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.79,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我拍張照片好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.42,0:13:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩再拍一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.59,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.11,0:14:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.55,0:14:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人出來旅行\N真的沒什麼浪漫可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是無聊而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.06,0:14:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也住在室生屋旅館吧\N早上我有看到妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.76,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了,接下來我想搭計程車\N去江戶村看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要不要跟我分擔車錢\N一起去呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.77,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太謝謝妳了\N我很擔心車錢可能不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說\N我也一個人正覺得無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有在上班嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊,我是公寓的管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.19,0:15:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛辭去上班族的工作\N現在是自由之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.96,0:15:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.48,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,我要拍囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.28,0:15:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣,來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.42,0:15:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,這是一點小禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.69,0:15:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,再見囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不抽菸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.67,0:15:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以這樣呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒看到這個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.71,0:15:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抽菸要去規定的地方抽\N知道了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.48,0:15:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.32,0:16:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我問你\N你腳下的那些是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.29,0:16:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我抽的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼\N到了這種地方還想抽菸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.13,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.17,0:16:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可別誤會,我不是在罵你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方拍張照片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.61,0:16:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得那棟房子前面怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,以後小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.26,0:16:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.33,0:16:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那好像是五代的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,這是不可能的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拍了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.27,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒有男朋友嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一定有個很棒的男朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.51,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.39,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我可能暫時無法和妳見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.23,0:17:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對妳已經沒有感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭,我怎麼想起了這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.04,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子只好去旅館門口等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要關門了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晴美,關門的時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.76,0:18:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人獨處的話,就會很想死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.57,0:18:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼說這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.68,0:18:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員怎麼還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.10,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,運氣真背\N要是能訂到同一間旅館就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在是旅遊旺季\N這也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.08,0:19:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為這個,辭去了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.72,0:19:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…是男性問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.99,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發旅行之前\N我還將旅行日程表寄給他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.79,0:19:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天的行程和時間\N都寫的很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.53,0:19:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳懂嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的江戶村\N是最後一個地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.48,0:19:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果好像是自己在唱獨角戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日程表啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.38,0:20:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜,我怎麼也開始胡思亂想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.24,0:20:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她到底去了哪裡?\N這麼晚還沒回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.02,0:21:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.85,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?派出所?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.56,0:21:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代的確是這裡的房客沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.86,0:21:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的,他啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.37,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你們說\N聽說五代被抓去警察局做筆錄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是不是偷了內褲啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.27,0:21:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豬頭,豬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有這個膽嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有沒有,他沒這個膽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.58,0:21:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼跟什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.83,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會\N不過,妳不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.10,0:21:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊,出來旅行果然是對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.17,0:21:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在心情好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.34,0:21:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.68,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.81,0:22:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.02,0:22:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多保重,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.85,0:22:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照預定行程表來看\N3點30分會到輪島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.52,0:22:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搭電車先過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.38,0:22:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.62,0:22:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開車囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.66,0:22:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.55,0:23:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人在幹嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要阻擾我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,你想去撞車自殺嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.46,0:23:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這個大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.39,0:23:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.90,0:23:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙,想違抗本官嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.27,0:23:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.91,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.72,0:23:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男…男女混浴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.25,0:23:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯,管理員和五代\N在男女混浴池湊巧遇見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.53,0:23:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是一絲不掛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會穿衣服泡溫泉的只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.93,0:23:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.53,0:24:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『太好了!和響子泡男女混浴\N露天溫泉兩人獨處』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.57,0:24:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.35,0:24:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.90,0:24:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.42,0:24:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.75,0:24:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.22,0:25:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.40,0:25:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.43,0:25:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.84,0:25:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.24,0:25:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
